text: hello everyone, I am stuck in an error from last 3-4 days: An error occurred (ValidationException) when calling the InvokeModel operation: Operation not allowed  when searched it, on internet I found this https://repost.aws/knowledge-center/bedrock-invokemodel-api-error , they have metioned: Account restriction error Error: "An error occurred (ValidationException) when calling the InvokeModel operation: Operation not allowed"  The error appears when your AWS account has a security restriction.  To resolve this issue, open a support case in AWS Support.
